## Rules
- profile_statement: 4-6 lines, lead with fit for {{ role }} at {{ company }}, achievements not duties
- For PM/Program Manager roles: include ≥3 phrases from must_have_keywords or keyword_placement_hints.summary
- Include category **Project & Program Management:** in competencies when role is PM/Program Manager
- Weave ATS keywords naturally (from targets) — only if supported by profile
- Avoid vague openers ("passion for innovation") without PM keywords from targets
- competency_keywords: 1-2 phrases to weave into EXISTING competency categories
- NEVER use company/city/job title alone as competency category

Return ONLY JSON:
{
  "profile_statement": "...",
  "competency_keywords": ["phrase from posting matched to profile"],
  "competencies": ["Executive Leadership: COO leadership, change management, KPI"],
  "tailoring_notes": ["1-2 short decisions"]
}
Each competencies entry MUST be a single string "Category: comma-separated skills" — NOT a JSON object.
